<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c2">(٥٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{نَاظِرِينَ إِنَاهُ}</span> ... مُنْتَظِرِينَ نُضْجَهُ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c2">(٥٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مَتَاعًا}</span> ... حَاجَةً مِنْ أَوَانِي البَيْتِ، وَنَحْوِهَا.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(٥٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{لَّا جُنَاحَ عَلَيْهِنَّ}</span> ... لَا إِثْمَ عَلَيْهِنَّ فِي عَدَم الاِحْتِجَابِ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(٥٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَلَا نِسَائِهِنَّ}</span> ...<span class="c5"> أَيِ:</span> النِّسَاءِ المُؤْمِنَاتِ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(٥٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مَا مَلَكَتْ أَيْمَانُهُنَّ}</span> ... العَبِيدِ المُمْلُوكِينَ لَهُنَّ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(٥٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{يُصَلُّونَ}</span> ...<span class="c5"> صَلَاةُ اللهِ:</span> ثَنَاؤُهُ عَلَى عَبْدِهِ فِي المَلَإِ الأَعْلَى،<span class="c5"> وَصَلَاةُ المَلَائِكَةِ:</span> ثَنَاؤُهُمْ وَدُعَاؤُهُمْ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(٥٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{يُؤْذُونَ اللَّهَ}</span> ... يُشْرِكُونَ بِهِ، وَيَعْصُونَهُ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(٥٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{لَعَنَهُمُ اللَّهُ}</span> ... أَبْعَدَهُمْ، وَطَرَدَهُمْ مِنْ كُلِّ خَيْرٍ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(٥٨)</span> ... <span class="c3">{احْتَمَلُوا}</span> ... ارْتَكَبُوا.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(٥٨)</span> ... <span class="c3">{بُهْتَانًا}</span> ... أَفْحَشَ الكَذِبِ وَالزُّورِ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">(٥٩)</span> ... <span class="c3">{يُدْنِينَ عَلَيْهِنَّ}</span> ... يُرْخِينَ عَلَى رُؤُوسِهِنَّ وَوُجُوهِهِنَّ وَصُدُورِهِنَّ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c2">(٥٩)</span> ... <span class="c3">{جَلَابِيبِهِنَّ}</span> ...<span class="c5"> الجِلْبَابُ:</span> الرِّدَاءُ، وَالمِلْحَفَةُ الَّتِي تَسْتُرُ بَدَنَ المَرْأَةِ وَزِينَتَهَا.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c2">(٥٩)</span> ... <span class="c3">{أَدْنَى}</span> ... أَقْرَبُ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c2">(٥٩)</span> ... <span class="c3">{أَن يُعْرَفْنَ}</span> ... يُمَيَّزْنَ بِالسِّتْرِ وَالصِّيَانَةِ؛ فَلَا يُتَعَرَّضَ لَهُنَّ بِمَكْرُوهٍ.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c2">(٦٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مَّرَضٌ}</span> ... شَكُّ، وَرِيبَةٌ.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span><span class="c2">(٦٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَالْمُرْجِفُونَ}</span> ... الَّذِينَ يَنْشُرُونَ الأَخْبَارَ الكَاذِبَةَ.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>